				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$K_{{\text{c }}} = \frac{P}{{\left( {\beta C^{3/2} } \right)}},$$\end{document}
where ‘β’ is the indenter constant taken as 7 for the Vickers indenter and ‘C’ is the length of crack measured from the center of the indentation mark to the crack end.

